{
  "texts": [
    "A more complete discussion of prompts for image generation is provided in [21] and [36].While each of these tools offers its own prompting interface, most are rather simple and basically consist of a free writing area to indicate the prompt and a visualization of the prompt execution.",
    "A few also execute prompts on the generative AI system and log the results for visualization or analysis.",
    "Nevertheless, there is no advanced support for the writing of the prompt itself via some type of prompt language or similar, nor a way to document and version a prompt.",
    "We discuss a few exceptions in the next subsection.",
    "Prompt buildersSome tools aim to assist the prompt engineer when writing the prompts, mostly to offer a taxonomy of a fixed set of prompt dimensions you can choose from when building your prompt."
  ]
}